results.name: Number of partitions with exactly n subpartitions.
comment: Conjecture that lim_{n->infinity} a(n) = infinity. Definitely a(n) > 2 for n > 8.
link: Niccolò Castronuovo, On the number of fixed points of the map gamma, arXiv:2102.02739 [math.NT], 2021. Mentions this sequence.
results.author: _Franklin T. Adams-Watters_, Mar 17 2006
